item.title: Tucson
item.description: Almost pulled a muscle laughing in the ride from the Tucson airport to our hotel. It’s only 5:30 here. Weird. That call that “time difference” for you lefties who read my blog. Has to do with the earth being round and all. Been a whirlwind day so far. Met Trent and Jennifer Humphries, remarkable Tea Party leaders here in Tucson. Most gracious hosts you can imagine. Funny, dedicated, joyous. After checking into hotel, I spoke to Mike Ferguson of Eagle 93.
